{"tid":114151,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"5日4夜東京行程求狠批","createTime":"2017-02-09T14:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T22:34:36.000Z","uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83213f07976017bedb6a588b50c3c5f8fae9b5bf","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"第一次去東京, 咩都唔識, 亂plan左個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday 1(日)：新宿(酒店) &gt; 係新宿9行<br />\nday 2(一)：新宿 &gt; 涉谷<br />\nday 3(二)：築地 &gt; 台場 &gt; tokyo tower<br />\nday 4(三)：自由之丘 &gt; 下北澤 &gt; 原宿<br />\nday 5(四)：去機場<br />\n<br />\n主要都係想食野同行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打們指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad0ab0416a147b6058882bd04e8245e67dcf7c7","tid":114151,"uid":53509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"自己鍾意原宿渋谷放埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁近，行過去都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957761e6e35838225aec78697c1cf7baff6f56ec","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己鍾意原宿渋谷放埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁近，行過去都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁近架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但一日行唔行得哂呀?"},{"pid":"128a7ad6961e67a38c44ab86110208782a52c4a0","tid":114151,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"行街可以加埋池袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  夠集中"},{"pid":"f5085bb76327eeb58836c9cb48a23852a9437291","tid":114151,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己鍾意原宿渋谷放埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁近，行過去都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁近架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但一日行唔行得哂呀?</blockquote><br />\n好近架 又可以去埋明治神宮 第一次無理由唔行下原宿既 又有竹下通"},{"pid":"1ed66d95a3ec7f699ae4693a8499ba9b009aa4a0","tid":114151,"uid":12417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:37:52.000Z","msg":"我三月頭都第一次去, 仲要自己一個去<br />\n咩都未plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3381b5df37a9716dce8fa0dc2d0429bfefeefa97","tid":114151,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"新宿行一日唔悶咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dae403e36513cdd9b8cba2368794673a07d2f0","tid":114151,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"樓主想睇服裝?"},{"pid":"fc23c2e1519eb2e6ec8d0f5550d629e11f9b9fad","tid":114151,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"浅草 上野 唔去？"},{"pid":"c37d9e22fd29f0c25202ea4a9fb315321159ade1","tid":114151,"uid":70343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"去左下北澤先會比較好<br />\n如果樓主你鐘意二手衫同古著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買到手都斷<br />\n東洋百貨 <br />\nmode off <br />\nnew york joes<br />\n好平<br />\n有錢可去big time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次去完下北澤幾乎無再係新原宿買過衫<br />\n同埋新宿其實無咩野行"},{"pid":"555fcdc0fa89f47c40046efef3322b746e825044","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行街可以加埋池袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  夠集中</blockquote><br />\n本身都想去, 但池袋好似冇乜野行<br />\n巴打有冇提議有咩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f02613c659d3a62b8e273e0cb55e65038c7655a","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新宿行一日唔悶咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭一日落機都2點啦, 去埋酒店乜乜77應該都4-5點喇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef17f5acfdb94781f35044f4480f203a3285caab","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主想睇服裝?</blockquote><br />\n衫褲鞋襪, 化妝品護膚品果D咩都想行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb2249619d984fe996d3974e0b7891be51764ee","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>浅草 上野 唔去？</blockquote><br />\n呢2個地方有咩玩有咩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf6df7a44d5a955ddaaf93a6c82e52c584e9709","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去左下北澤先會比較好<br />\n如果樓主你鐘意二手衫同古著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買到手都斷<br />\n東洋百貨 <br />\nmode off <br />\nnew york joes<br />\n好平<br />\n有錢可去big time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次去完下北澤幾乎無再係新原宿買過衫<br />\n同埋新宿其實無咩野行</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea29315838bfee22a04714bf688e91224c979cb2","tid":114151,"uid":71703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次去東京, 咩都唔識, 亂plan左個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday 1(日)：新宿(酒店) &amp;gt; 係新宿9行<br />\nday 2(一)：新宿 &amp;gt; 涉谷<br />\nday 3(二)：<span style=\"color: red;\">築地 &amp;gt; 台場 &amp;gt; tokyo tower</span><br />\nday 4(三)：自由之丘 &amp;gt; 下北澤 &amp;gt; 原宿<br />\nday 5(四)：去機場<br />\n<br />\n主要都係想食野同行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打們指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅字 我果時都係咁去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夜晚睇東京鐵塔好正!<br />\n不過比我揀我鐘意 原宿,竹下通,表參道果堆多過涉谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1bf77e7d22126f82a54b4882d6052a3bcc84a7","tid":114151,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>浅草 上野 唔去？</blockquote><br />\n呢2個地方有咩玩有咩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上野: 動物園, 阿美橫丁<br />\n淺草: 雷門寺, 仲見世通"},{"pid":"bbb6975190fd7db9e02b6cb8ae70428ef55969ef","tid":114151,"uid":70343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去左下北澤先會比較好<br />\n如果樓主你鐘意二手衫同古著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買到手都斷<br />\n東洋百貨 <br />\nmode off <br />\nnew york joes<br />\n好平<br />\n有錢可去big time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次去完下北澤幾乎無再係新原宿買過衫<br />\n同埋新宿其實無咩野行</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果鐘意wego<br />\n建議係下北澤店買<br />\n覺得好過原宿總店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藥妝新宿大把 <br />\nuniqlo一蘭嗰頭有一間啲化妝品牌好齊架<br />\n不過咁多 我咁講你都未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n東京鐵塔未去過<br />\n但覺得係六本木roppongi hills睇可能仲正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9znRh1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9znRh1z.jpg&h=f7ced330&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e0a2c22357abd5b6a0ec06f11d3576a59cb25e5","tid":114151,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>浅草 上野 唔去？</blockquote><br />\n呢2個地方有咩玩有咩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上野: 動物園, 阿美橫丁<br />\n淺草: 雷門寺, 仲見世通</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上野仲有2定3間美術館 就算唔睇去行下恩賜公園都唔錯<br />\n淺草寺前面條路 同埋外圍都好適合買手信<br />\n<br />\n覺得第一次去東京唔去呢兩個地方好似差左啲野咁 反而覺得台場冇咩好睇<br />\n不過睇你想chur定想hea啦"},{"pid":"7d94ebfed8e63c69fe2c8b8b7ca6418c533352b0","tid":114151,"uid":53509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去左下北澤先會比較好<br />\n如果樓主你鐘意二手衫同古著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買到手都斷<br />\n東洋百貨 <br />\nmode off <br />\nnew york joes<br />\n好平<br />\n有錢可去big time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次去完下北澤幾乎無再係新原宿買過衫<br />\n同埋新宿其實無咩野行</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果鐘意wego<br />\n建議係下北澤店買<br />\n覺得好過原宿總店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n藥妝新宿大把 <br />\nuniqlo一蘭嗰頭有一間啲化妝品牌好齊架<br />\n不過咁多 我咁講你都未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n東京鐵塔未去過<br />\n但覺得係六本木roppongi hills睇可能仲正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9znRh1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9znRh1z.jpg&h=f7ced330&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n六本木hills個景勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過建議去之前了解下點樣隔住塊玻璃影相都唔反射先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鍾意行街的話吉祥寺都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附近仲有宮崎俊個館同井之頭公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5afb83cced09c9c45e5b8d81aba8b4caadef921","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一次去東京, 咩都唔識, 亂plan左個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday 1(日)：新宿(酒店) &amp;amp;gt; 係新宿9行<br />\nday 2(一)：新宿 &amp;amp;gt; 涉谷<br />\nday 3(二)：<span style=\"color: red;\">築地 &amp;amp;gt; 台場 &amp;amp;gt; tokyo tower</span><br />\nday 4(三)：自由之丘 &amp;amp;gt; 下北澤 &amp;amp;gt; 原宿<br />\nday 5(四)：去機場<br />\n<br />\n主要都係想食野同行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打們指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅字 我果時都係咁去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夜晚睇東京鐵塔好正!<br />\n不過比我揀我鐘意 原宿,竹下通,表參道果堆多過涉谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講表參道都係high end野多?"},{"pid":"dfd32c6426b600ec1fd078e6d420fedfa441ed97","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>浅草 上野 唔去？</blockquote><br />\n呢2個地方有咩玩有咩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上野: 動物園, 阿美橫丁<br />\n淺草: 雷門寺, 仲見世通</blockquote><br />\n我睇睇先, 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a320bf3b9f3a166b5ab66015739f1376af4ef7","tid":114151,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>浅草 上野 唔去？</blockquote><br />\n呢2個地方有咩玩有咩行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor